{"tid":1496262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：香港局勢不會成為貿談因素習近平可人道解決","createTime":"2019-08-22T12:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T12:48:57.000Z","uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"07f598494913f96b5120f50889db8f6ae60a08e1","tid":1496262,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普說，香港局勢不會成為影響中美貿易談判的一個因素。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，中國國家主席習近平有能力，確保在香港混亂的抗議活動，能夠以人道方式解決。<br />\n<br />\n另外，加拿大總理杜魯多亦再次談及香港問題，呼籲相關各方克制，展開對話。在北京，外交部批評加方妄議香港事務，要求停止干涉中國內政。"},{"pid":"617adf0c70b549b52d09265c30e5926603660daa","tid":1496262,"uid":161193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0bd7550de7660e2fed7aa6901343ab5e527191","tid":1496262,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:23:09.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f2cd0cfd00a0087e781cb020f5817eaec7718f","tid":1496262,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:29:36.000Z","msg":"習總唔玩爛個場<br />\n侵都唔會點用香港牌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（但其實已經用緊）"},{"pid":"03c6bb1a03352e7edc522a80ca31620c975d85cc","tid":1496262,"uid":185126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"撚狗撚到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36762dd896e8784d2b68a3ef7bb4fece459a42f7","tid":1496262,"uid":70336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:40:26.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入先似佢，自己香港自己救。完。"},{"pid":"602eb2dd95e7556a26d15f3e9adfe252cf1654e0","t